    <h3>Zilla Slab</h3>
    <p>Zilla Slab is our core typeface. We use it for our wordmark, for headlines, and throughout our designs. It’s a contemporary slab serif based on Typotheque’s Tesla. It’s constructed with smooth curves and true italics, which gives text an unexpectedly sophisticated industrial look and a friendly approachability in all weights. Zilla Slab is a free, open source font available for download.</p>

